  "thig5.10:0.1": "",
  "thig5.10:0.2": "",
  "thig5.10:0.3": "",
  "thig5.10:1.1": "[I thought:] “Plowing the field with plows,",
  "thig5.10:1.2": "sowing the ground with seed,",
  "thig5.10:1.3": "supporting their wives & children,",
  "thig5.10:1.4": "young men gather up wealth.",
  "thig5.10:2.1": "So why is it that I, consummate in virtue,",
  "thig5.10:2.2": "a doer of the teacher’s bidding,",
  "thig5.10:2.3": "don’t gain unbinding?",
  "thig5.10:2.4": "I’m not lazy or proud.”",
  "thig5.10:3.1": "Washing my feet, I noticed the water.",
  "thig5.10:3.2": "",
  "thig5.10:3.3": "",
  "thig5.10:3.4": "And in watching it flow from high to low,",
  "thig5.10:4.1": "my heart was composed",
  "thig5.10:4.2": "like a fine thoroughbred steed.",
  "thig5.10:4.3": "Then taking a lamp, I entered the hut,",
  "thig5.10:4.4": "",
  "thig5.10:4.5": "checked the bedding,",
  "thig5.10:4.6": "sat down on the bed.",
  "thig5.10:5.1": "And taking a pin, I pulled out the wick:",
  "thig5.10:5.2": "",
  "thig5.10:5.3": "Like the flame’s unbinding",
  "thig5.10:5.4": "was the liberation of awareness.",
  "thig5.10:6.1": ""
}